    missionEyebrow: "OUR MISSION",
    missionTitle: "Going in His name.",
    missionP1: "Two-thirds of God’s name is GO, and every commanding moment in history is connected to the word GO. God’s only Son was a missionary. He left a secure, heavenly home to GO to another world and culture to share the Good News with us.",
    missionP2: "The word GO was so vital that Jesus himself came back from the grave to remind us to “GO into all the world and share the Gospel. GO teach all nations.” For more than 40 years, in literal obedience to His command, we have gone with one goal in mind.",
    missionStatement: "Our relentless aim is to love and teach children to know, love and serve Jesus.",
    artTitle: "Every child matters.",
